      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just worry about the side effects of the pills though. i've been feeling a bit nauseous and my stomach is weird. if i'm already feeling 100% better physically, isn't it safer to just stop the drugs now rather than risking more stomach issues or other side effects for no reason? if the infection is gone, the risk of the medicine might actually be higher than the benefit at this point, right?",
